      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I also want to touch on the idea of \"property rights\" in this. Like, if a platform is private, the government shouldn't be able to mandate how they moderate content because that's basically seizing control of private property. Can you expand on the libertarian view of digital property rights as a defense against regulation?",
